Takes a username, domain, email, or IP address and performs OSINT reconnaissance using public sources/APIs like:

🔎 Username search across platforms (GitHub, Twitter, Reddit)

🧠 Email breach check using HaveIBeenPwned

🕵️ Domain info (WHOIS, DNS, subdomain brute force)

🌐 IP geolocation and reputation

🧪 LinkedIn/Google dork recon (optional)

